replies.body:
" Veigar has lost his way competing against mobile champions "

Veigar has a 60% wr against Akali. A 55% wr against Yas and a 54% wr against Irelia a 61% wr against Azir and a 57% wr wr against Galio but alrighty. Ironically enough Veig struggles the most against early game pokers{{champion:74}} {{champion:115}} {{champion:136}} 

Veigars current problem is that he doesnt have a reliable keystone. He doesnt need more dmg or slows, he needs survivability. Phage rush is so awful because it doesnt work on burst so you cant R and run away like with stormrazor. Maybe next season something that fits Veigar will be introduced.
